# ============================================================================
# Sensitive material — never commit these.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Master vault stores: VaultBox runs at %LOCALAPPDATA%\VaultBox\vault.db
# and exports as *.vaultbox; KeePass exports as *.kdbx; we also catch the
# common Bitwarden / 1Password / Chrome export shapes in case someone drops
# one in the working tree by mistake during a debug session.
# ============================================================================
vault.db
vault.db-shm
vault.db-wal
vault.db-*
*.vaultbox
*.kdbx
*.kdb
bitwarden_export*.json
bitwarden_export*.csv
bitwarden-export*.json
bitwarden-export*.csv
chrome_passwords*.csv
1password_export*.1pux
1password_export*.1pif
*-export-*.json
*-export-*.csv

# Catch-all for keys / certs / secrets that don't already match *.pem.
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.pkcs12
*.cer
*.crt
*.gpg
*.asc

# Environment / secret files.
.env
.env.*
secrets.json
credentials.json
auth.json

